OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Fsome patchy rain or showers this
OL,7,Fevening. It will stay cloudy overnight
OL,8,Fwith more general outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fspreading from the west, some becoming
OL,10,Fheavy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,13,Foccasional rain, some heavy, then
OL,14,Fbrightening up during the afternoon
OL,15,Fwith some sunny spells, and becoming
OL,16,Fwarm.
